==English==

===Suffix===
'''-mancy'''
# specified forms of [[divination]]

===Derived suffixes===

*''-mance:'' to carry out a specified form of divination
*''-mancer:'' a person who employs a specified form of divination
*''-mantic:'' of or pertaining to a specified form of divination

